Jinja2 raise extension

Extend Jinja2 envrionment with a raise method so that
we can add logic in Jinja2 and raise errors.

In jinja2 template the raise method can be used like this:

 {%- if condition %}
   {{ raise('MESSAGE') }}
 {%- endif %}

